divs: Sighting Detailsi was walking home and i saw this flying in the sky. i was going to go to the balcony to see if it was still flying around but it was gone. i first noticed it by seeing the lights. i thought it was plane at first, but none of the lights were flashing and there was about 5 lights going around it in a circle. it was flying really fast and turning. i was kind of excited and scared when i saw the ufo.
Summary: black, with yellowish white lights. was flying in a circle fast and quietly
